Property of type: `string`.

 
The following are valid values for the `status` property:
  + `temporary`
  + `running`
  + `pending`
  + `pending_launch`
  + `initializing`
  + `importing`
  + `terminated`
  + `pending_terminate`
  + `suspended`
  + `pending_suspend`
  + `resuming`

To filter on this field, use: `status=...`.


